In the cinema he was a director and screenwriter of the films 'Smoke', directed together with Wayne Wang, and 'Blue in the Face'. In 1998 he directed 'Lulu on the Bridge', starring Willem Dafoe and Harvey Keitel.<br> His last novel, 'Baumgartner', was released in 2023, coinciding with the announcement of his illness. In Italy his works were published by Einaudi.&nbsp;

